Since IBM service desk could not resolve the issue with VPN:

Cisco Anyconnect can not connect to secure gateways issue

Many of You and I could randomly encounter for weeks – I have found solution.

On win 7 please go co  Start > Click Computer to see Manage (right click) – then  Services and Applications > Services > 
then search for ICS – Internet Connection Sharing and STOP it and also set startup type to DISABLED. 
